items.description:
* Annual Recurring Charge  $360.00 

* Fixed monthly charge = Annual Recurring Charge / 12
Annual accounts will be billed in advance for service.  The annual recurring charge will be billed immediately upon metering being made available to the member and prorated to the next billing date.  Billing for the annual recurring charge will be billed on or before May 1st of each year.  Meters will be read on an annual basis on or before October 31st.  Energy charge bills will be calculated based on the actual usage and mailed to the members by the first day of the following month.  Payment is due by the 10th day following the billing date.  All payments for service must be in U.S. funds.
